            "name": "Topics in Monetary Economics - Honours",
            "title": "<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/econ-459\" target=\"_blank\">ECON 459</a> Topics in Monetary Economics - Honours (3 credits)",
            "overview": "Economics (Arts) : An advanced treatment of selected topics in monetary economics, including the theory and practice of monetary policy.",
