            "name": "Parallel Computing",
            "title": "<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-420\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 420</a> Parallel Computing (3 credits)",
            "overview": "Electrical Engineering : Modern parallel computing architectures for shared memory, message passing and data parallel programming models. The design of cache coherent shared memory multiprocessors. Programming techniques for multithreaded, message passing and distributed systems. Use of modern programming languages and parallel programming libraries.",
            "terms": "Terms: Fall 2019",
