            "notes": "<p>(2-4-3)</p>\n\n<p>Prerequisites: <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-221\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 221</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-222\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 222</a> and <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-334\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 334</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-331\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 331</a> and <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-352\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 352</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-353\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 353</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-354\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 354</a></p>\n",
