            "title": "<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-450\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 450</a> Electromagnetic Compatibility (3 credits)",
            "overview": "Electrical Engineering : Electromagnetic Compatibility (EMC), regulations and EMC requirements of electronic systems, non-ideal behaviour of circuit components, signal spectra, radiated emission and susceptibility, conducted noise, crosstalk, differential mode and common mode, shielding, and system design for EMC.",
