            "notes": "<p>(3-2-4)</p>\n\n<p>Prerequisite: <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-323\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 323</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/ecse-325\" target=\"_blank\">ECSE 325</a></p>\n",
