            "overview": "Electrical Engineering : A laboratory design project undertaken with close supervision by a staff member. A continuation of ECSE 474 Design Project 1. The work consists of carrying out the project plan developed in ECSE 474 Design Project 1 producing a report summarizing the results, and a seminar presentation.",
