            "notes": "<p>Prerequisites: <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/math-315\" target=\"_blank\">MATH 315</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/math-325\" target=\"_blank\">MATH 325</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/math-263\" target=\"_blank\">MATH 263</a>; <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/math-317\" target=\"_blank\">MATH 317</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/math-387\" target=\"_blank\">MATH 387</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/comp-350\" target=\"_blank\">COMP 350</a> or <a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/mech-309\" target=\"_blank\">MECH 309</a>; or permission of the instructor</p>\n\n<p>This course will be taught in the winter semester.</p>\n",
