            "name": "Geometric Group Theory",
            "title": "<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/math-583\" target=\"_blank\">MATH 583</a> Geometric Group Theory (4 credits)",
            "overview": "Mathematics &amp; Statistics (Sci) : Actions on trees. Cayley graphs. The word problem. Hyperbolic groups. Quasi-isometry invariants.",
