            "name": "Advanced Probability Theory 1",
            "title": "<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/math-587\" target=\"_blank\">MATH 587</a> Advanced Probability Theory 1 (4 credits)",
            "overview": "Mathematics &amp; Statistics (Sci) : Probability spaces. Random variables and their expectations. Convergence of random variables in Lp. Independence and conditional expectation. Introduction to Martingales. Limit theorems including Kolmogorov's Strong Law of Large Numbers.",
