            "title": "<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/math-327\" target=\"_blank\">MATH 327</a> Matrix Numerical Analysis (3 credits)",
            "overview": "Mathematics &amp; Statistics (Sci) : An overview of numerical methods for linear algebra applications and their analysis. Problem classes include linear systems, least squares problems and eigenvalue problems.",
