            "title": "<a href=\"https://mcgill.ca/study/2019-2020/courses/math-592\" target=\"_blank\">MATH 592</a> Mathematical Logic 2 (4 credits)",
            "overview": "Mathematics &amp; Statistics (Sci) : Introduction to recursion theory; recursively enumerable sets, relative recursiveness. Incompleteness, undecidability and undefinability theorems of Gödel, Church, Rosser and Tarski. Some of the following topics: Turing degrees, Friedberg-Muchnik theorem, decidable and undecidable theories.",
